Package: nba
Title: Facilitate access to the NBA API.
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: person("Imad", "Ali", email = "imad.ali@columbia.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The NBA package provides functions that make it easy for R users to access the NBA API (stats.nba.com). It also provides court plotting functions to facilitate shot chart data visualization.
Depends: 
  R (>= 3.4.0),
  rjson (>= 0.2.15),
  dplyr (>= 0.7.2),
  sp (>= 1.2.5),
  raster (>= 2.5.8)
Suggests:
    roxygen2,
    testthat (>= 1.0.2)
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
